item.description:
Jonathan's Lounge has started its annual karaoke contest, culminating in finals in May, which I have posted as a meetup event the previous 2 years. The winner from Jonathan's Lounge will compete against other winners in a nationwide contest with other winners from karaoke contests in bowling alley lounges.

Each week until then, they are holding preliminary contests each Wed. and Sat., in which 1 finalist is selected each night. If you don't win, you can compete as many nights as you want.

The judges are the dj and all previous winners who are in attendance that night.

This is one of those preliminary contest nights. There is no entry fee.

There will be regular karaoke both before and after the contest.

I will be competing.

I am listing this event for several meetup groups.
item.name: karaoke (contest AND regular)
